Signals 2014 focuses on green economy, resource efficiency and circular economy. We are extracting and using more resources than our planet can produce in a given time. Current consumption and production levels are not sustainable and risk weakening our planet\ufffd\ufffd\ufffds ability to provide for us. We need to reshape our production and consumption systems to enable us to produce the same amount of output with less resource, to re\ufffd\ufffd\ufffduse, recover and recycle more, and to reduce the
